Careers

Halo Companies, Inc. is comprised of hard-working individuals dedicated to serving the financial needs of our customers. We are always looking for sharp, motivated people to join our team. Requests for employment opportunities can be sent to info@haloco.com.
Halo Companies, Inc. and its subsidiaries (“Halo”) are equal opportunity employers and do not discriminate on the basis of any legally protected status or characteristic. Nothing in this site constitutes a promise or offer of employment.

Halo Companies Culture
At Halo Companies, there is a mutual respect among the team that fosters growth, collaboration and innovative thinking. In the end, it is our excellent culture that reaps the rewards of our close-knit relationships.
Commitment to Excellence
Halo Companies is committed to excellence. We believe our purpose and guiding principles are the keys to our success and we look for individuals who share them.
PURPOSE
To Help People.
GUIDING PRINCIPLES

 Value Relationships
Hold respect, loyalty and trust as the highest tenants of relationships and believe that life is all about loving your fellowman. Relationships are built by developing, mentoring and serving others.
 Do the Right Thing
Allow purpose, integrity and passion to guide all decisions. 
 Go Above and Beyond
Thrive on exceeding expectations and never be content to simply do what is expected. Long term value is created by finding ways to improve the business and the lives of others. Be passionate about making a difference.

These guiding principles help us attract the most talented, enthusiastic and professional people in the marketplace who fit our culture. Once hired, we do everything we can to keep them, including promoting from within, offering a compensation program that provides an opportunity to make a great living, and providing affordable benefits.





