Vendor Management

Comprehensive Vendor Management
Halo’s comprehensive vendor management capabilities allow for the aggregation of service provider data and communications into a single, streamlined access point of information. As the asset manager, Halo contracts with national, tier 1 service providers to reduce costs, improve efficiencies and maintain necessary regulatory compliance and licensing. Service providers are fully integrated into Halo’s software platform for seamless workflow and improved insight for asset management clients. 
Maintaining the highest level of service from vendors is an imperative factor in the performance of an asset. Halo carefully selects the most reliable, well-respected national and local vendors in the industry to ensure quality service is delivered to clients in the following areas:

 Property preservation
 Valuation services
 Title reports
 Property tax status / tracking
 Mobile notary services
 Document custodial services
 Default resolution
 Skip tracing
 File imaging and indexing
 Credit reporting
 Inspection services






