LAN, Telecom, DC/DC Converter Transformers | HALO Electronics











































Close window [X]   
	























Products




HALO Electronics designs and manufactures signal and power magnetics for LAN, telecom, DC/DC converter circuits, and high voltage isolation applications.  HALO’s products are UL recognized, manufactured in ISO9001 factories, 100% tested, and designed to meet and exceed the industry standards.  Choose HALO as your one stop shop for all your magnetics needs. If you don’t see a product that meets your requirements please contact the factory for additional solutions.

